::Rex/Firearm::

Rex looks as Battera and Hakibuscon depart, setting the defences to once 
again recognize them as enemy. He looks at Firearm as he receives 
Triceradon's transmission. "You wanna go help him?"

Firearm nods. "Sure," he says, transforming into tank mode and driving off 
north.

Rex turns, entering the Cybertronian Fire and walking toward Battera's 
quarters.
